body_html:
Have you tried the suggestion on this stack overflow page? It suggest that the issue may be related to CUDA/cudnn.

Try to rename cudnn64_6.dll to cudnn64_5.dll in C:\Program Files\NVIDIA GPU Computing Toolkit\CUDA\v8.0\bin.

https://stackoverflow.com/questions/43577923/cannot-import-tensorflow-for-gpu-on-windows-10.
